EN: This celebrity does charity work and also adopts orphans.

ZH: 收养流浪狗需要有责任心。
EN: Adopting a stray dog requires responsibility.

ZH: 她决心收养这个无家可归的小男孩。
EN: She is determined to adopt this homeless little boy.

ZH: 他们无法生育自己的孩子，所以决定收养一个。
EN: They cannot have their own children, so they decided to adopt one.

ZH: 许多名人都在积极宣传动物收养。
EN: Many celebrities actively promote animal adoption.

